<section id='aviso-section'>
  <input type='checkbox' id='aviso-cerrar' style='display:none;' />
  <div class='aviso-content'>
    <header>
      <span class='icono'>
        <svg
          width='24'
          height='24'
          viewBox='0 0 28 28'
          fill='none'
          xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'>
          <circle cx='14' cy='14' r='13' fill='#fffbe6' stroke='#e6c800' stroke-width='2'></circle>
          <path d='M14 8v7' stroke='#e6c800' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round'></path>
          <circle cx='14' cy='19' r='1.5' fill='#e6c800'></circle>
        </svg>
      </span>
      <h3>ATENCIÓN</h3>
      <label for='aviso-cerrar' class='close' aria-label='Cerrar aviso' tabindex='0' role='button'
        >&times;</label
      >
    </header>
    <p>
      Los acordes han sido migrados automáticamente desde el blog antiguo. Puede haber errores de
      acordes cortados, fuera de sitio o perdidos. Si detectas alguno, <a href='/contacto'>
        avísanos</a
      >.
    </p>
  </div>
  <style>
    section {
      display: none !important;
      position: absolute;
      top: 16px;
      right: 12px;
      z-index: 20;
      max-width: 340px;
      background: #fffbe6;
      color: #7a5c00;
      border: 1px solid #ffe58f;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      padding: 12px 40px 12px 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    #aviso-section:has(#aviso-cerrar:checked) {
      display: none !important;
    }
    header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #e6c800;
      margin: 0 0 2px 0;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      & .icono {
      }
    }

    p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #7a5c00;
      line-height: 1.1;

      & a {
        color: var(--link-color);
        font-weight: bold;
        text-decoration: none;

        &:hover {
          color: var(--link-hover-color);
        }
      }
    }
    .close {
      background: none;
      border: none;
      color: #7a5c00;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      position: absolute;
      top: 8px;
      right: 10px;
      line-height: 1;
      padding: 0;
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      section {
        max-width: 220px;
        top: 6px;
        right: 6px;
        padding: 12px;
      }

      svg {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
      }
      header {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</section>
